definitions: The eighth letter of the alphabet.
Denoting the next after G in a set of items, categories, etc.
Denoting the file on the right-hand edge of the board, as viewed from White's side.
A shape like that of a capital H.
(in the German system) the note B natural.
the constant of proportionality relating the energy of a photon to its frequency
a thermodynamic quantity equal to the internal energy of a system
plus the product of its volume and pressure.
